---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Arya's NoteBook">
  <h1 class="wel">Hi, Welcome...!</h1>

  <h3 class="wel-sub">All posts</h3>

  <span class="sp"
    >I'm Abhikr passionate about AI, open source, and I want to share some
    blogs.</span
  >

  <hr class="sep-hr" />

  <h2 class="feat">Featured</h2>

  <section>
    <h4 class="p1">
      <u>
        Windows 11 development environment out-of-the-box configuration process.
      </u>
    </h4>
    <div class="cla">
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="24"
        height="24"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="#ffffff"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        class="lucide lucide-calendar-days-icon lucide-calendar-days"
        ><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect
          width="18"
          height="18"
          x="3"
          y="4"
          rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path><path d="M8 14h.01"
        ></path><path d="M12 14h.01"></path><path d="M16 14h.01"></path><path
          d="M8 18h.01"></path><path d="M12 18h.01"></path><path d="M16 18h.01"
        ></path></svg
      >
      <span>28 Jan, 2026 | 07:30 PM</span>
    </div>
    <p>
      It's been almost a year since I ran out of articles, so let's talk about
      how this year's popular language model collided with GraphQL through MCP
    </p>
  </section>
    <section>
    <h4 class="p1">
      <u>
        Fix VSCode Remote SSH remote connection glibc high version dependency
      </u>
    </h4>
    <div class="cla">
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="24"
        height="24"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="#ffffff"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        class="lucide lucide-calendar-days-icon lucide-calendar-days"
        ><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect
          width="18"
          height="18"
          x="3"
          y="4"
          rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path><path d="M8 14h.01"
        ></path><path d="M12 14h.01"></path><path d="M16 14h.01"></path><path
          d="M8 18h.01"></path><path d="M12 18h.01"></path><path d="M16 18h.01"
        ></path></svg
      >
      <span>28 Jan, 2026 | 07:30 PM</span>
    </div>
    <p>
      I feel that macOS development is not smooth, and I usually have to consider playing games, but of course, All in One uses Windows 11 to solve development and entertainment
    </p>
  </section>

  <style>
    .wel {
      font-size: 40px;
    }
    .sp {
      font-style: oblique;
    }
    .cla {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .cla svg {
      flex-shrink: 0; /* Prevents icon from shrinking */
    }

    .wel-sub {
      font-size: 20px;

      color: azure;
    }

    .feat {
    }
    .p1 {
      font-style: initial;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: rgb(204, 151, 237);
    }
    .sep-hr {
      border-color: rgb(192, 133, 247);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
